*ppp-2.4.1-r8 (09 Apr 2002)

  22 May 2002; Mike Jones <ashmodai@gentoo.org> :
  Added (optional - USE crypt variable was used) MPPE support for ppp, enabling
  clients who use the pptp server to have encrypted connections.

